Product Sales Ranking Analysis 
-This query ranks products based on their total sales performance.
Purpose of the query
-Identify top-selling products
-Compare product performance using rankings

SELECT
    p.product_name,
    SUM(s.sales_amount) AS total_sales,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(s.sales_amount) DESC) AS sales_rank
FROM sales s
JOIN product p ON s.product_id = p.product_id
GROUP BY p.product_name;

-Aggregates sales amount for each product
-Uses the RANK() window function to assign a rank
-Products with the same sales receive the same rank
-Joins sales transactions with product details
-Ensures each sale is associated with the correct product
-Groups records at the product level
-Required for aggregation before ranking
